   <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
      <p class="- topic/p ">The purpose of this procedure is to protect personnel by establishing a system for identifying confined spaces, evaluating the potential hazards associated with these spaces and developing safe entry procedures. This establishes the minimum requirements to ensure the safe entry and work within all confined spaces.</p>
